OL,3,CWhy the US could be setting its sights
OL,4,Con Kharg Island
OL,6,FWords by ITV News' Lucy L. Middleton
OL,8,FUS President Donald Trump has
OL,9,Fconfirmed he is considering a ground
OL,10,Finvasion of Iranian oil hub, Kharg
OL,11,FIsland, despite ongoing negotiation
OL,12,Ftalks between the countries.
OL,14,FMore than 2,500 US marines began
OL,15,Farriving in the region over the last
OL,16,Fweek of March, with thousands more on
OL,17,Ftheir way.
OL,19,F"Maybe we take Kharg Island, maybe we
OL,20,Fdon't. We have a lot of options,"
OL,21,FTrump told the Financial Times.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1774947927
OL,3,CWhy the US could be setting its sights
OL,4,Con Kharg Island
OL,6,F"It would also mean we had to be there
OL,7,Ffor a while."
OL,9,FThe president had previously said the
OL,10,FUS could "take out" the island
OL,11,F"anytime we want", telling reporters
OL,12,Fit was "so totally unprotected".
OL,14,FITV News takes a closer look.
OL,16,FWhy is Kharg Island important?
OL,18,FKharg Island is Iran's primary oil hub
OL,19,F- the terminal for nearly all of
OL,20,FIran's seaborne oil exports.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1774947927
OL,3,CWhy the US could be setting its sights
OL,4,Con Kharg Island
OL,6,FMeasuring just five miles in length,
OL,7,Fit is surrounded by much deeper water
OL,8,Fthan Iran's coastline, meaning the
OL,9,Fworld's largest tankers can berth
OL,10,Fthere.
OL,12,FThis makes it Iran's main loading,
OL,13,Fcollection and storage point for crude
OL,14,Foil, and a complex network of
OL,15,Fpipelines connects the island with
OL,16,Fonshore Iranian processing facilities.
OL,18,FAround 94% of Iran's crude exports
OL,19,Foriginated from Kharg in the last 12
OL,20,Fmonths, data analytics company Kpler
OL,21,Fshowed.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1774947927
OL,3,CWhy the US could be setting its sights
OL,4,Con Kharg Island
OL,6,FThe terminal has remained active
OL,7,Fduring the war, and handled 14 million
OL,8,Fbarrels of crude oil during the first
OL,9,Ftwo weeks of March, generating revenue
OL,10,Ffor the Islamic Revolutionary Guard
OL,11,FCorps (IRGC).
OL,13,F"He who controls Kharg Island,
OL,14,Fcontrols the destiny of this war," US
OL,15,FSenator Lindsey Graham, a close ally
OL,16,Fof Trump, posted on X on March 14.
OL,18,FAbout 20,000 people are reported to
OL,19,Flive on the island, with most being
OL,20,Foil workers and their families.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1774947927
OL,3,CWhy the US could be setting its sights
OL,4,Con Kharg Island
OL,6,FIs the island protected?
OL,8,FKharg Island is sometimes referred to
OL,9,Fas "Forbidden Island" due to its
OL,10,Fextreme security.
OL,12,FThe IRGC Navy maintains a presence on
OL,13,Fthe land, including the 112th
OL,14,FZolfaghar Surface Combat Brigade, a
OL,15,Funit equipped with fast-attack boats
OL,16,Fthat have anti-ship missiles, rockets
OL,17,Fand naval mines.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1774947927
OL,3,CWhy the US could be setting its sights
OL,4,Con Kharg Island
OL,6,FIt is also reported to have ground-
OL,7,Fbased air defence units comprising of
OL,8,Flaunchers, radars, and control
OL,9,Fcentres, and bunkers for naval mines
OL,10,Fand missiles.
OL,12,FHas the US struck the island before?
OL,14,FThe US bombed Kharg Island during the
OL,15,Fsecond week of the war - and Trump
OL,16,Fissued a warning it would strike again
OL,17,Fif the Strait of Hormuz is not
OL,18,Freopened fully.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
