OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1774947927
OL,3,CWhy the US could be setting its sights
OL,4,Con Kharg Island
OL,6,FUS Central Command claimed it had
OL,7,Fdestroyed naval mine storage
OL,8,Ffacilities and missile storage bunkers
OL,9,Fin the attack.
OL,11,FIran's semi-official Fars news agency
OL,12,Fsaid the strikes had caused no damage
OL,13,Fto oil infrastructure, but an air
OL,14,Fdefence facility, naval base, airport
OL,15,Fcontrol tower and helicopter hangar
OL,16,Fbelonging to an offshore oil company
OL,17,Fhad been targeted.
OL,19,FWhat impact could a further attack
OL,20,Fhave?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1774947927
OL,3,CWhy the US could be setting its sights
OL,4,Con Kharg Island
OL,6,FAn attack or seizure of Kharg Island
OL,7,Fwould "send the oil price into a spin"
OL,8,Fand significantly escalate the war,
OL,9,Fenergy policy expert Dr Neil Quilliam
OL,10,Ftold ITV News.
OL,12,FAttacking the island would take away
OL,13,FIran's capacity to export high volumes
OL,14,Fof oil, and retaliatory strikes from
OL,15,Fthe regime on energy infrastructure in
OL,16,Fthe Gulf states would also have long-
OL,17,Fterm implications, Dr Quilliam said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31810
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1774947927
OL,3,CWhy the US could be setting its sights
OL,4,Con Kharg Island
OL,6,F"This would push the immediate price
OL,7,Fhigher, (but) it would also mean that
OL,8,Fthe global economy would experience
OL,9,Fthe loss of oil and natural gas from
OL,10,Fmarkets for much longer, as the
OL,11,Frecovery time would probably takes
OL,12,Fmany months, if not years," he said.
OL,14,FIran has vowed to avenge any action
OL,15,Ftaken on Kharg Island, with a military
OL,16,Fsource telling IRGC-affiliated Tasnim
OL,17,FNews the regime would block other
OL,18,Fvital waterways such as the Bab al-
OL,19,FMandab Strait and the Red Sea, if it
OL,20,Fwas invaded.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
