OL,4,Con Kharg Island
OL,6,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FThe speaker of the Iranian parliament
OL,12,Falso warned that vital infrastructure
OL,13,Fin the region ` including energy and
OL,14,Fdesalination facilities ` would be
OL,15,F"irreversibly destroyed" if his
OL,16,Fcountry's own infrastructure was
OL,17,Fattacked.
