OL,3,CWhy the US could be setting its sights
OL,4,Con Kharg Island
OL,6,FEarlier in March, the president
OL,7,Fdeclared that the US could "take out"
OL,8,FKharg Island "anytime we want",
OL,9,Ftelling reporters at the White House
OL,10,Fon Friday the land was "totally
OL,11,Funprotected".
OL,13,FWhen asked about a planned invasion or
OL,14,Fblockade of Kharg, the White House's
OL,15,Fpress secretary said the US could
OL,16,Fattack the island "if the president
OL,17,Fgives the order".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
