OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1774947927
OL,3,CWhy the US could be setting its sights
OL,4,Con Kharg Island
OL,6,FIran's parliament speaker warned that
OL,7,Fthe Iranian military would set any
OL,8,Finvading US troops "on fire" and
OL,9,F"punish their regional partners
OL,10,Fforever", in a statement published
OL,11,Fthrough state media on Sunday.
OL,13,F"The enemy publicly sends messages of
OL,14,Fnegotiation and dialogue while
OL,15,Fsecretly planning a ground attack,"
OL,16,FMohammad Bagher Ghalibaf said via the
OL,17,Fofficial Islamic Republic News Agency.
OL,19,F"Our firing continues. Our missiles
OL,20,Fare in place. Our determination and
OL,21,Ffaith have increased."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G17/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
