CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1774947927
OL,3,CWhy the US could be setting its sights
OL,4,Con Kharg Island
OL,6,FGhalibaf had previously denied direct
OL,7,Ftalks were taking place with the US,
OL,8,Fcalling it "fake news" that is
OL,9,F"intended to manipulate financial and
OL,10,Foil markets to escape the quagmire in
OL,11,Fwhich America and Israel are trapped".
